# Aerospace Embedded Software Experience

## Overview

Experience working on safety-critical embedded software development for Rolls-Royce aircraft engine control systems supporting Airbus programs under DO-178B/C development processes.

## Responsibilities

* Developed and maintained embedded software using Ada 95 and C
* Worked on Maintenance, Fault Management, Stall Detection, and Interactive Reporting components
* Performed code modifications, debugging, impact analysis, and verification support
* Maintained software traceability and configuration management activities
* Applied SPARK 95 static analysis techniques for runtime error verification
* Supported review resolution, DV updates, and compliance-related activities

## Technologies & Tools

* Ada 95
* Embedded C
* DO-178B/C
* SPARK 95
* PTC Integrity
* Artisan Studio
* Git/GitHub

## Areas Worked

* Fault Management
* Interactive Reporting
* Maintenance Systems
* Development Variables (DV)
* Software Verification
* Traceability Support

## Skills Gained

* Safety-Critical Software Development
* Real-Time Embedded Systems
* Verification & Validation
* Configuration Management
* Requirements Traceability
* Embedded Software Debugging
